# Portfolio Project Summary

## Project Overview
Building a modern portfolio website using Next.js, TypeScript, and Tailwind CSS. The site showcases Spencer Tigere as a software developer who builds business solutions.

## Current Features Implemented

### 1. Navigation Component (`app/components/Navigation.tsx`)
- **Sliding text animation**: "Spencer Tigere" slides to "(software developer)" on hover
- **Color transition**: Text changes from gray to orange-500 on hover
- **Smooth animation**: 1000ms duration with ease-in-out timing
- **Compact container**: w-48 width for precise hover detection

### 2. BalloonDemos Component (`app/components/BalloonDemos.tsx`)
- **Static 2D circles** (reverted from 3D spheres)
- **Hover expansion**: Circles scale to 110% on hover
- **Color change**: Circles turn orange-400 on hover
- **Centered layout**: Three demo cards side by side
- **Clickable**: Each circle links to respective demo pages

### 3. LetterDisplay Component (`app/components/LetterDisplay.tsx`)
- **Fixed hydration issue**: Uses deterministic random numbers for consistent server/client rendering
- **Animated text**: Letters have individual speed values for drift effects

### 4. Custom Cursor (`app/components/CustomCursor.tsx`)
- **Physics-based movement**: Inertia effect like a ball on a string
- **Smooth animation**: 60fps with spring physics
- **Invisible physics objects**: No visual clutter, just smooth movement

### 5. Scroll Indicator (`app/components/ScrollIndicator.tsx`)
- **Bottom right positioning**: Fixed at bottom-right corner
- **Auto-hide**: Disappears when user scrolls down 20% of viewport
- **Bouncing arrow**: Animated down arrow with bounce effect

## Page Structure (`app/(site)/page.tsx`)
1. **Animated Text Section**: LetterCollision component
2. **About Section**: Profile image (circular, 400px) + description
3. **Featured Projects**: BalloonDemos component
4. **Hero Section**: Title + CTA buttons

## Styling Preferences
- **Color scheme**: Blue (#3B82F6) primary, Orange (#F59E0B) for hover states
- **Typography**: Clean, modern fonts with good hierarchy
- **Layout**: Responsive design with proper spacing
- **Animations**: Smooth transitions (300-1000ms) with ease-in-out timing

## Key Technical Decisions
- **No continuous movement**: Prefer static elements with hover interactions
- **Simple physics**: Use for subtle effects (cursor, not main content)
- **Performance focus**: Optimized animations and clean code
- **Accessibility**: Proper hover states and clickable areas

